               <p>1786. <persName id="def1-1786-18450818" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def1-1786-18450818" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1786-18450818" type="age" value="21"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1786-18450818" type="surname" value="HOPKINS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1786-18450818" type="given" value="MATTHEW"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">MATTHEW HOPKINS</hi>
                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18450818-1786-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450818-1786-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450818-1786-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18450818-cd-55" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1786-offence-1 t18450818-cd-55"></join>13th of Aug</rs>., 6 tame pigeons, price 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the property of <persName id="t18450818-name-1098" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1098" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1098" type="surname" value="FREELAND"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1098" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450818-1786-offence-1 t18450818-name-1098"></join>Thomas Freeland</persName>; and that he had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450818-name-1099" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1099" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1099" type="surname" value="FREELAND"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1099" type="given" value="GEORGE WILLIAM"></interp>GEORGE WILLIAM FREELAND</persName>
                  </hi>. I am fourteen years old—my father,</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184508180190"></xptr>
               <p>Thomas Freeland, lives in Smith-street, Camberwell. On the 13th of Aug., about five o'clock in the morning, I missed six pigeons from a pigeon-house at the back of my father's house—I had seen them safe at nine o'clock the night before—I have seen five of them since.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. HUDDLKSTON</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Did you buy them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> My father did—they were rather common—he had had them six months—they were in a dove-cote—they flew about, but they went in the cote at night, and were shut up.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450818-name-1100" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1100" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1100" type="surname" value="ATTWOOD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1100" type="given" value="JANE"></interp>JANE ATTWOOD</persName>
                  </hi>. At half-past eight o'clock in the morning of the 13th of Aug. the prisoner brought me six tame pigeons—I bought them of him—five of them are here.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined. Q.</hi> He told you a man named Jones sent him with them? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes, and he said he lived in Thomas-street—he did not say Thomas-street, Kennington.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450818-name-1101" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1101" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1101" type="surname" value="NEAL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1101" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN NEAL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable P</hi> 30.) I took the prisoner—I said the charge was for taking some pigeons—he said, "Very well, I will go with you"—I produce the pigeons.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450818-name-1102" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1102" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1102" type="surname" value="DAVIES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450818-name-1102" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD DAVIES</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable P</hi> 55.) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 18th March, 1844; confined three monthst and whipped</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18450818-1786-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
